Ratings: Ratings / release decade / Platform (histogram) + Ratings / Platform "What is the difference between ratings on the various platforms and year?"

Content Creation: TV Shows and Movies by platform by year (Line graph) + Total Titles by platform by year (Line graph) "Is the amount of content produced increasing or decreasing? Is it different by TV / Movie?"
  
Movie Duration: Movie Runtime by 5-year bin (histogram) + Movie Runtime by year (Scatterplot) "Is movie runtime increasing or decreasing over time?"

TV Show Duration: Season count broken by Platform + Season count broken by Category
"What are the TV shows with the most seasons on each platform?"
